Class EntailmentRelation<T extends Formula>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.tweety.commons.EntailmentRelation<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of formula the relation works on.

    public abstract class EntailmentRelation<T extends Formula>
extends Object
    An entailment relation determines whether a formula is entailed from another formula.

    Matthias Thimm
